"""Inverse of Undo[x] is Redo[x]"""
graph_operation = GraphEditOperation.from_log_record(cg, FakeLogRecords.
    UNDO.record)
inverted_graph_operation = graph_operation.invert()
assert isinstance(inverted_graph_operation, RedoOperation)
assert graph_operation.superseded_operation_id == inverted_graph_operation.superseded_operation_id
